Feature: PatternExpressionAcceptance

  Scenario: Returning an `extract()` expression
    Given an empty graph
    And having executed:
      """
      CREATE (a:A)
      CREATE (a)-[:T]->(:B),
             (a)-[:T]->(:C)
      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH (n)
      RETURN extract(x IN (n)-->() | head(nodes(x))) AS p
      """
    Then the result should be:
      | p            |
      | [(:A), (:A)] |
      | []           |
      | []           |
    And no side effects

